  <Notes>
    <Note Caller="1" LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="" LastEditedBy="">
      <References/>
      <Content>In a number of contexts it is difficult to determine whether the focus of σάρκινος[c] and σαρκικός[c] is upon the natural, physical characteristics or upon the tendency to behave in a particular way. In any event, resulting behavior is always implied.</Content>
    </Note>
    <Note Caller="2" LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="" LastEditedBy="">
      <References>
        <Reference>04600300300006</Reference>
        <Reference>04600300300026</Reference>
      </References>
      <Content>The close proximity of σάρκινος and σαρκικός in the context of  {S:04600300100000}-{S:04600300300000} would seem to indicate that there is little, if any, difference in meaning.</Content>
    </Note>
